OL,3,CMum accused of murder admits caning
OL,4,Cson after watching religious video
OL,6,FA mother standing trial accused of her
OL,7,Fson's murder has admitted beating the
OL,8,Fthree-year-old with a cane, leaving
OL,9,Fhim alone in the house with his
OL,10,Fyounger brother and failing to seek
OL,11,Fimmediate medical help for severe
OL,12,Fburns.
OL,14,FChristina Robinson, 30, denies causing
OL,15,Fa fatal injury to her son Dwelaniyah
OL,16,Fby violently shaking him at the family
OL,17,Fhome in Bracken Court, Ushaw Moor,
OL,18,FDurham, in November 2022.
