OL,3,CMum accused of murder admits caning
OL,4,Cson after watching religious video
OL,6,FShe is accused of hitting him with a
OL,7,Fbamboo cane and deliberately scalding
OL,8,Fhim, causing excruciating burns to his
OL,9,Flegs and buttocks, in the weeks before
OL,10,Fhis death.
OL,12,FThe defendant, who is originally from
OL,13,FTamworth, Staffordshire and who grew
OL,14,Fup for a period in Bulgaria, denies
OL,15,Fmurder and a child cruelty charge.
OL,17,FGiving evidence in the witness box at
OL,18,FNewcastle Crown Court for the first
OL,19,Ftime on Wednesday 13 March, Robinson
OL,20,Ftold the court of events on the day he
OL,21,Fdied.
