OL,3,CMum accused of murder admits caning
OL,4,Cson after watching religious video
OL,6,FWearing a black shawl and grey jumper
OL,7,Fdress, she said she was watching TV
OL,8,Fwith Dwelaniyah and her other son when
OL,9,Fthere was a "gargling, gasping" sound
OL,10,Fas he "lolled to the side".
OL,12,FThe little boy had been eating a
OL,13,Fcheese bap, she said, adding that she
OL,14,Fremoved the food that had been
OL,15,Fobstructing his airway before
OL,16,Fcommencing CPR.
OL,18,FThe court has previously been told
OL,19,Fthat Dwelaniyah died as a result of
OL,20,Fmajor head injury caused by him being
OL,21,Fshaken, or a head impact, or both.
