OL,3,CMum accused of murder admits caning
OL,4,Cson after watching religious video
OL,6,FRobinson suggested in court that he
OL,7,Fhad fallen "on his face" a few days
OL,8,Fbefore and that day had fallen twice.
OL,10,FShe also admitted it took 19 minutes
OL,11,Fbetween her son collapsing and her
OL,12,Fcalling 999.
OL,14,FThe defendant also told the jury said
OL,15,Fthat she follows a religious movement
OL,16,Fcalled the "Black Hebrew Israelites".
OL,18,FThe court has heard Dwelaniyah was
OL,19,Ffound with 19 long thin bruises on his
OL,20,Fbody.
