OL,6,FShe admitted she hit son Dwelaniyah
OL,7,Fwith a garden cane after watching
OL,8,Fteachings in a YouTube video,
OL,9,Fdisciplining him on the day he died
OL,10,Fbecause "he was messing about with his
OL,11,Ffood".
OL,13,FThis she told the jury was a decision
OL,14,Fshe now believed was "misguided".
OL,16,FRobinson also told the court burns to
OL,17,Fthe lower half of his body had been
OL,18,Fcaused accidentally with a shower.
