OL,6,FThe court previously heard that after
OL,7,FDwelaniyah's collapse on the day he
OL,8,Fdied, Robinson told the emergency
OL,9,Fservices his burns had been caused by
OL,10,Fhim playing in the shower.
OL,12,FBut the jury was told by the defendant
OL,13,Fthat that was not true. She told the
OL,14,Fcourt they were instead a result of
OL,15,Fher cleaning him after he had soiled
OL,16,Fhimself.
