OL,6,FShe told jurors: "I already felt
OL,7,Fashamed at the time when it happened,
OL,8,FI didn't mean to do this to him.
OL,10,F"As it got worse and worse, it just
OL,11,Flooked really bad. I knew it would
OL,12,Flook really bad."
OL,14,FThe trial has previously heard experts
OL,15,Fdescribe Dwelaniyah's burns as "a
OL,16,Ftextbook" example of "non accidental"
OL,17,Finjuries caused by a child being
OL,18,Fimmersed into scalding hot water.
