OL,6,FThe defendant was also questioned in
OL,7,Fcourt about her personal situation
OL,8,Fduring which time she told the jury
OL,9,Fshe wanted to have a family with more
OL,10,Fthan 10 children.
OL,12,FThe court also heard Robinson said her
OL,13,Fmarriage to Dwelaniyah's father,
OL,14,FGabriel Adu-Appau, was failing after
OL,15,Fhe decided to join the RAF.
OL,17,FShe told the jury she looked into
OL,18,Fusing a sperm donor after the
OL,19,Frelationship "broke up".
