OL,6,FJamie Hill KC, defending, asked how
OL,7,Fmany children she wanted to have.
OL,9,F"Double figures," she replied.
OL,11,FShe also said she was prepared to be a
OL,12,Fsurrogate mother for a friend, saying
OL,13,Fshe was "very fertile", but in the
OL,14,Fend, it was not necessary as the woman
OL,15,Fgot pregnant herself.
OL,17,FMr Hill asked who did the discipline
OL,18,Fin the house if both parents were
OL,19,Fthere and the defendant answered that
OL,20,Fit was her husband.
