OL,3,CMum accused of murder admits caning
OL,4,Cson after watching religious video
OL,6,FShe claimed he used shoes, a sandal,
OL,7,Fslippers, utensils or pieces of wood
OL,8,Fto discipline in the house.
OL,10,FRobinson told the jury that after one
OL,11,Foccasion, she had told her husband
OL,12,F"that was unnecessary" but that "it
OL,13,Fwas as if what I had said did not
OL,14,Fmatter".
OL,16,FRobinson said she had discussed
OL,17,Fphysical punishments with her husband,
OL,18,Fwho grew up in Ghana, and she told the
OL,19,Fcourt: "He explained to me and told me
OL,20,Fstories about how things were done
OL,21,Fwhere he came from."
