OL,6,FThe court has heard Mr Adu-Appau was
OL,7,Faway from the family home, serving on
OL,8,Fan RAF base near Aylesbury when
OL,9,FDwelaniyah was fatally injured.
OL,11,FRobinson said she had four
OL,12,Fmiscarriages but her husband only knew
OL,13,Fabout two of them, adding: "He wasn't
OL,14,Finterested, he didn't care that they
OL,15,Fdied."
OL,17,FShe added: "It was a hard time for me,
OL,18,Fand I never have and I never will
OL,19,Frecover from them."
